Now there are a few more
things you should know

00:18:31.446 --> 00:18:32.636 A:middle
about automatic signing.

00:18:33.886 --> 00:18:36.396 A:middle
The first one is that it
does development signing.

00:18:37.116 --> 00:18:39.546 A:middle
Distribution is handled
through a different workflow;

