created provisioning profile.

00:18:47.216 --> 00:18:49.846 A:middle
These of course are profiles
Xcode makes on your behalf,

00:18:50.166 --> 00:18:51.456 A:middle
and it keeps them up-to-date

00:18:51.636 --> 00:18:53.316 A:middle
as you're working
on your application.

00:18:53.916 --> 00:18:58.876 A:middle
And as a result of these,
you can use automatic signing

00:18:59.046 --> 00:19:00.406 A:middle
without ever having to worry


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:18:59.046 --> 00:19:00.406 A:middle
without ever having to worry

00:19:00.406 --> 00:19:04.246 A:middle
about your distribution signing
assets being touched by Xcode.

00:19:05.086 --> 00:19:06.616 A:middle
So your distribution certificate

00:19:06.616 --> 00:19:09.036 A:middle
and provisioning profile
will never be modified

00:19:09.036 --> 00:19:10.096 A:middle
by automatic signing.

00:19:12.136 --> 00:19:14.436 A:middle
So automatic signing.

00:19:14.436 --> 00:19:16.736 A:middle
It's been completely
redesigned in Xcode 8.

00:19:17.366 --> 00:19:20.886 A:middle
It stays out of your way,
and it manages signing.

00:19:21.216 --> 00:19:23.266 A:middle
So you can focus on
what's really important,

00:19:23.266 --> 00:19:26.376 A:middle
which is developing your app.

00:19:27.306 --> 00:19:29.296 A:middle
Now let's take a look at
the other side of the fence.

00:19:29.356 --> 00:19:30.486 A:middle
Customized signing.

00:19:31.516 --> 00:19:34.536 A:middle
As you'll recall, this is a
mode where you have full control

00:19:34.536 --> 00:19:35.816 A:middle
over how your app is signed.

00:19:36.416 --> 00:19:40.706 A:middle
You can enable customized
signing

00:19:41.076 --> 00:19:43.726 A:middle
by unchecking the checkbox
in the General tab.

00:19:44.866 --> 00:19:46.426 A:middle
And once you've done that,

00:19:46.426 --> 00:19:49.516 A:middle
Xcode will let you choose
different provisioning profiles

00:19:49.516 --> 00:19:51.286 A:middle
for each of your
build configurations.

00:19:52.516 --> 00:19:55.576 A:middle
This is really handy if you have
a continuous integration system.

00:19:55.576 --> 00:19:57.896 A:middle
Or you need different
profiles for free

00:19:57.896 --> 00:19:59.076 A:middle
and paid versions of your app.

00:19:59.506 --> 00:20:00.876 A:middle
Now you have the
power to do that.


WEBVTT
