you more helpful information

00:20:28.956 --> 00:20:31.466 A:middle
about that before you
run into those issues.

00:20:32.426 --> 00:20:35.086 A:middle
So we've added new
error reporting right

00:20:35.086 --> 00:20:36.176 A:middle
within the General tab.

00:20:36.626 --> 00:20:38.956 A:middle
And you can see this right
alongside your settings.

00:20:39.316 --> 00:20:41.216 A:middle
So it's easier to
