And you can choose
any type of profile.

00:21:34.176 --> 00:21:37.236 A:middle
So as I mentioned, if you want
to use development profiles

00:21:37.236 --> 00:21:40.376 A:middle
for some build configurations,
and distribution profiles

00:21:40.376 --> 00:21:45.766 A:middle
for others, you're
free to do that.

00:21:45.976 --> 00:21:47.236 A:middle
Now this is a really cool thing.

00:21:47.236 --> 00:21:49.956 A:middle
Especially for those of
you experienced developers

00:21:49.956 --> 00:21:52.126 A:middle
who have manually chosen
profiles in the past.

